bodyEn:
1. My IMPS transfer Rs. {AMOUNT} (UTR {UTR}) on {TXN_DATE} was rejected by the beneficiary bank. The reverse credit has not reached my account even after the standard T+1 IMPS settlement window. Please trace the failed-batch and credit the amount immediately.

Attachments: UPI transaction screenshot, PSP complaint acknowledgement, bank statement extract for the debit.

Regards,
{USER_NAME}
Mobile: {MOBILE_NO}

bodyHi:
1. मेरा IMPS ट्रांसफर Rs. {AMOUNT} (UTR {UTR}) दिनांक {TXN_DATE} को लाभार्थी बैंक ने अस्वीकार कर दिया। मानक T+1 IMPS settlement window बाद भी reverse credit मेरे खाते में नहीं आया। कृपया failed-batch trace कर राशि तुरंत जमा करें।

संलग्न: UPI लेनदेन स्क्रीनशॉट, PSP शिकायत स्वीकृति, बैंक स्टेटमेंट अंश।

भवदीय,
{USER_NAME}
मोबाइल: {MOBILE_NO}
